(182, 1, '2012-03-29 20:28:21', '2012-03-29 20:28:21', '<h2>Mission</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://anthropology.cos.ucf.edu/include/image/anthro/hominids_logo_1.jpg" alt="logo" width="150" height="116" />\r\n\r\nThe mission of Hominids Anonymous is to provide a social and educational environment for UCF students interested in Anthropology to meet and share ideas. Our goal is to promote and facilitate education, research, and local activity in Anthropology. The organization aims to explore all subfields of Anthropology through various group activities and weekly discussions.\r\n\r\nFirst meeting of Spring will be held at the gazebo in front of the bookstore at 4:30 Tues 1/17. Weekly meetings to be held every Tuesday at 4:30 - Room TBA.\r\n\r\nCheck out our website at <a href="http://hominidsanonymous.org/">HominidsAnonymous.org</a>\r\n\r\nSearch for the Hominids Anonymous group page on Facebook!\r\n\r\nContact us via E-mail: <a href="mailto:annab@knights.ucf.edu">annab@knights.ucf.edu</a> / <a href="mailto:creightonfain@gmail.com">creightonfain@gmail.com</a>', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'anthro-club', '', '', '2012-04-16 14:21:52', '2012-04-16 14:21:52', '', 15, 'http://localhost/COS%20Dept/?page_id=182', 0, 'page', '', 0),
